            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美伊和談露曙光，戰火有望平息，激勵台股今 (1) 日強勢反彈，記憶體、矽智財、PCB 及低軌衛星等族群全面噴漲，帶動盤中最高漲至 33182.22 點，漲逾千點，終場大漲 1451.83 點或 4.58%，創台股第二大漲點，以 33174.82 點作收，一舉站回 33000 點關卡，也同步收復 5 日線與季線，距離月線 33230 點僅一步之遙，成交量 6161.23 億元。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6404275/l/90247899c861f8f7fc1eb91ece2f0bd7.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉創史上第二大漲點 噴漲1451點站回3萬3 差點攻克月線。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察電子權值股今天表現，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 漲 95 元，大漲逾半根停板，收 1855 元，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 也都漲逾半根停板，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 強攻漲停鎖死 361 元，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 也漲逾 4%。不過聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 今天表現獨自黯淡，跌逾 1%。 </p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>記憶體族群今天漲勢凌厲，多檔高掛紅燈，旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>)、群聯 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8299:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8299\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8299-TW</a>)、宜鼎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5289:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5289\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5289-TW</a>)、宇瞻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8271-TW</a>)、威剛 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3260:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3260\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3260-TW</a>) 強攻漲停，南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)、創見 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>)、十銓 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4967:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4967\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4967-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>) 則漲逾 3%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>矽智財 (IP) 族群今天也有所表態，世芯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3661-TW</a>) 漲停鎖死 2730 元，創意 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，晶心科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6533:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6533\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6533-TW</a>)、宏觀 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6568:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6568\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6568-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，力旺 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3529:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3529\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3529-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，智原 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3035:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3035\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3035-TW</a>)、M31(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6643:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6643\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6643-TW</a>) 及巨有科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:8227:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8227\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8227-TW</a>) 皆漲逾 2%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>ABF 載板三雄紅通通，欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)、南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>) 漲停鎖死，景碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3189-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板。其他 PCB 族群表現同樣亮眼，金像電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2368:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2368\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2368-TW</a>) 亮燈漲停，台燿 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6274-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，低軌衛星族群也走揚，正文 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4906:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4906\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4906-TW</a>) 強攻漲停，仲琦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2419:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2419\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2419-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，啟碁 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6285:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6285\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6285-TW</a>)、昇達科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3491:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3491\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3491-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，耀登 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3138:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3138\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3138-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過在類股全面通紅中，唯獨造紙類股一點綠，近日漲多的華紙 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1905:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1905\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1905-TW</a>) 慘跌停，榮成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1909:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1909\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1909-TW</a>) 跌逾半根停板，正隆 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1904:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1904\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1904-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%，永豐餘 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1907:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1907\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1907-TW</a>) 也跌逾 1%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
